    "title": "Kuamini Nguvu za Binadamu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kuamini nguvu za binadamu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu mara nyingi alionyesha nguvu zake kwa watu wake katika historia yao. Aliwafanya wazee wawili, ambao hawakuweza kupata watoto, kuwa mababu wa taifa kubwa. Aliwaokoa watu hawa kutoka kwa mtawala mwenye nguvu wa Misri. Alifanya miujiza mingi kuwasaidia kuishi jangwani.</p><p>Pia walipata ushindi dhidi ya maadui zao mara nyingi wakati wa kipindi cha Waamuzi na kipindi cha wafalme. Hata hivyo, katika historia yao yote, watu wa Israeli mara nyingi hawakumwamini Bwana. Walichagua kutegemea nguvu za kibinadamu badala yake.</p><p>Wakati mmoja, Asa, Mfalme wa Yuda, alimwomba mfalme wa Aramu msaada. Aramu alikuwa adui wa muda mrefu wa watu wa Mungu. Asa alimpa hazina kutoka hekalu na ikulu ili amshambulie Baasha, Mfalme wa Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:1-2Chr16:6\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 16:1–6</a>). Nabii Hanani alimkosoa Asa, akimwonya kwamba Aramu angeendelea kuwa adui wa Yuda. Vita vya zamani vilionyesha kwamba Asa alihitaji Mungu pekee kama msaada (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:8\">16:8</a>).</p><p>Kutegemea kwa Asa kwa mfalme wa Aramu kulionyesha tatizo la kina la kiroho. Asa alisahau kwamba &quot;macho ya Bwana huzunguka huku na huko juu ya dunia yote&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:9\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 16:9</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:10\">Zekaria 4:10</a>). Wakati Hanani alipomwonyesha Asa makosa yake, Asa alimfunga nabii gerezani haraka. Mfalme mwenye hasira pia aliwadhuru watu bila haki (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:10\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 16:10</a>).</p><p>Asa anaonyesha jinsi watu mara nyingi hutegemea rasilimali zao wenyewe na kukasirika wanapokosolewa (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:7\">Mithali 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1\">Isaya 31:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5-Jer17:6\">Yeremia 17:5–6</a>). Hata wale ambao wameona nguvu za Bwana wanaweza kutenda kwa njia hii. Hii ilikuwa kweli kwa Waisraeli waliokombolewa kutoka utumwani Misri. Ni bora kumtumaini Bwana na kukubali mwongozo wake (linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:18\">Zaburi 33:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:7\">37:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:10\">Isaya 50:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7-Jer17:8\">Yeremia 17:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:43\">Matendo 13:43</a>).</p><p>Maisha hutufundisha kumtumaini Mungu. Tunaweza kuanza kwa kutenda mema na haki (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:1-2Chr14:6\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 14:1–6</a>). Hata hivyo, athari yetu ya kiroho haijakamilika hadi tufikie hatua yetu ya mwisho (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:6-Rom2:11\">Warumi 2:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:1-1Cor4:5\">1 Wakorintho 4:1–5</a>). Hatupaswi kuruhusu tamaa za kibinafsi kudhoofisha uaminifu wetu kwa Ufalme wa Mungu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:4\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:15-2Kgs6:18\">2 Wafalme 6:15–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:1-2Chr16:10\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 16:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:7-2Chr32:8\">32:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:6-Ps20:8\">Zaburi 20:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3-Ps37:7\">37:3–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps60:11-Ps60:12\">60:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:7-Prov11:8\">Mithali 11:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10-Prov18:12\">18:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:14\">Mhubiri 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1-Isa31:5\">Isaya 31:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5-Jer17:8\">Yeremia 17:5–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:26-Matt10:31\">Mathayo 10:26–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:6-Rom2:11\">Warumi 2:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:1-1Cor4:5\">1 Wakorintho 4:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:8-Rev2:11\">Ufunuo 2:8–11</a></p>",
